1
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:40,850
[Fated Hearts]

2
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,990
[Episode 35]

3
00:02:01,759 --> 00:02:02,530
Your Highness,

4
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:03,710
the Imperial Guards are here.

5
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,770
Quite a few of them.

6
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:07,230
It must be the Murong family's doing.

7
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,070
Your Highness,

8
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,350
take Miss Yixiao and leave first.

9
00:02:09,350 --> 00:02:10,220
We'll take care of them.

10
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:10,980
Stay calm.

11
00:02:11,350 --> 00:02:12,360
They came prepared.

12
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,620
We mustn't act rashly.

13
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,050
They outnumber us.

14
00:02:15,050 --> 00:02:16,280
We can't fight them head-on.

15
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,150
Let's retreat for now.

16
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:17,760
Follow me.

17
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:18,690
But...

18
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,670
This way.

19
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:34,380
Search!

20
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:35,140
Yes!

21
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:39,560
Let's go.

22
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,240
Anyone there?

23
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,240
-No.
-No.

24
00:02:58,750 --> 00:02:59,420
General,

25
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,480
no one inside.

26
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:03,130
General, no one behind the house either.

27
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:09,620
Come on.

28
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:36,010
Murong Jie!

29
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:40,750
Attack!

30
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:52,700
Go report to General.

31
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:53,240
Yes.

32
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,480
This strike...

33
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:40,000
Is for Gu Yu!

34
00:04:47,150 --> 00:04:48,310
This strike

35
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:49,780
is for Hound!

36
00:04:58,340 --> 00:04:59,560
This strike...

37
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:04,240
Is for all our fallen brothers!

38
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:14,480
Kill!

39
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:35,360
Lu Ke.

40
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,159
We can't delay any longer.

41
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:39,890
Retreat now.

42
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,530
Let's go.

43
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,750
Keep chasing them!

44
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:13,110
Yes!

45
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:13,960
Let's go!

46
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,010
Yes!

47
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:21,690
Your Highness,

48
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,300
what should we do next?

49
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,560
Go to the Feng Battalion.

50
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,420
Your Highness,

51
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,650
I told you before

52
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,240
that in the Feng Battalion,

53
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,310
those who refused to submit to Murong Yao

54
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:33,830
have all been killed by him.

55
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,480
The Feng Battalion

56
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,830
is no longer what it used to be.

57
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:38,630
It would be dangerous for you to go there
like this.

58
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:40,159
Our men have fought through life and death

59
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,510
alongside me for so many years.

60
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:43,270
I don't believe they would betray me.

61
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:44,920
They only submitted to Murong Yao

62
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,380
by force of circumstance.

63
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,560
Be loyal to the ruler and the kingdom,

64
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,830
and never fail the people.

65
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,790
This is the shared belief of all our men.

66
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:53,430
This will never change.

67
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,180
The Feng Battalion

68
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,730
will always be the Feng Battalion.

69
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,510
You personally told me back then

70
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,909
that Feng Suige was dead,

71
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:07,030
and now you're telling me
he's still alive?

72
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:08,880
I killed him with my own hands,

73
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,250
and his body

74
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:12,050
was buried by Yao personally.

75
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:14,040
I cannot figure out

76
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,040
how he survived.

77
00:07:17,650 --> 00:07:19,510
Could it be that
Ling Feng went to save him?

78
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:21,310
It doesn't matter who saved him!

79
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,560
What matters is that he's still alive

80
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,490
and he's back!

81
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,610
He's back for revenge.

82
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:27,870
Your Majesty,

83
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,680
please calm down.

84
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,350
How can I possibly calm down?

85
00:07:31,870 --> 00:07:33,920
Back then, you asked me to save your son.

86
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,310
I made him a commandery prince

87
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:37,510
and even put the Imperial Guards
under his command.

88
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,720
Your Murong family

89
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,250
has gained so much already.

90
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:42,190
But what have you done in return?

91
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,990
A Feng Suige who has lost everything

92
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:47,960
is enough to make Your Majesty
panic like this?

93
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,010
If I could kill him once,

94
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,720
I can do it again.

95
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,480
But you've already made me

96
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,810
trust you wrongly once.

97
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,270
Feng Suige

98
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,890
hasn't even made a move yet,

99
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,480
and Your Majesty is already

100
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,270
trying to settle scores with me?

101
00:08:03,270 --> 00:08:05,870
It hasn't been long
since Feng Pingcheng died,

102
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,920
and you've already forgotten

103
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,850
how I helped you settle matters

104
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,080
and put your son

105
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,480
on the throne?

106
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,040
You're threatening me again.

107
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,170
This isn't a threat.

108
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,560
It's a reminder,

109
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,270
reminding Your Majesty

110
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,730
not to forget that you said

111
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,890
the Zhuang and Murong families

112
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,800
would forever be bound together,

113
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,070
sharing weal and woe.

114
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,870
Then I must also remind you

115
00:08:31,870 --> 00:08:33,040
that the one

116
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:36,570
who branded Feng Suige
with the crime of regicide and patricide

117
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,870
was you.

118
00:08:38,950 --> 00:08:40,750
You're truly battle-hardened.

119
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:43,270
You really know
how to keep your composure.

120
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:44,820
When Feng Suige returns,

121
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,030
the truth will be revealed.

122
00:08:47,789 --> 00:08:49,750
Given the situation,
you're still not worried,

123
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,320
so why should I be?

124
00:08:54,870 --> 00:08:55,670
Very well.

125
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:59,030
Now that everything's out in the open,

126
00:08:59,030 --> 00:09:01,120
it'll actually be easier for us
to handle things.

127
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,970
You and I

128
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,600
no longer have to pretend

129
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,720
to get along.

130
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,320
The closeness between our two families

131
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,670
may be a facade,

132
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,840
but the fact that we share weal and woe

133
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,840
is true.

134
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:15,920
As long as Feng Suige lives,

135
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,900
neither of us will know peace.

136
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:21,480
If Feng Suige

137
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,030
wants to turn things around,

138
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:24,720
he has only two paths to take:

139
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,660
the first is

140
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:26,840
to return now

141
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,630
and regain control of the Feng Battalion.

142
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:30,830
Your Majesty need not worry about this.

143
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,270
I can take care of it.

144
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,610
But this second path

145
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,570
concerns His Majesty the Emperor...

146
00:09:36,570 --> 00:09:38,030
Chengyang won't help him.

147
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,270
I'm his mother.

148
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,980
Your Majesty is so confident.

149
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:43,960
How many lies

150
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:46,450
did you tell His Majesty?

151
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:48,550
And how many of those lies did he buy?

152
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,330
Do you know

153
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:52,390
that His Majesty left the palace
last night

154
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:54,240
to see Feng Suige?

155
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,120
Did he

156
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,670
tell you about that?

157
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:00,720
What did you say?

158
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:07,310
Brother.

159
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,130
What else can I do for you?

160
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:12,520
Consider it

161
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,300
as me doing something for Father.

162
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,200
If that's the case,

163
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,000
I need you to do something for me.

164
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,520
Go and reclaim the command of

165
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,750
the Imperial Guards from

166
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:23,810
the Murong family.

167
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:25,470
All right.

168
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:27,710
I promise you.

169
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,930
Her Majesty the Empress Dowager
has arrived.

170
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:45,800
Everyone leave.

171
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:46,480
Yes.

172
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,030
Mother.

173
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,200
You left the palace last night.

174
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,210
Where did you go?

175
00:11:04,110 --> 00:11:05,440
I was feeling troubled,

176
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:07,630
so I wanted to go out for a walk.

177
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,980
You still dare to lie to me?

178
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,110
I'm the Emperor!

179
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,070
I go wherever I want!

180
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,810
So now you realize who you are?

181
00:11:16,490 --> 00:11:18,390
Now you know you're the Emperor?

182
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:20,270
Even if you're the Emperor,

183
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:21,870
you'll always be my son!

184
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:24,380
I'm the one who put you on that throne.

185
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,320
Is this imperial arrogance you're showing

186
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,910
meant for me?

187
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,420
Then I might as well

188
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,960
give up this throne.

189
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,020
You wouldn't dare!

190
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:33,640
Mother, you came to see me today

191
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,630
because you already knew

192
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:36,480
where I went

193
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,520
and whom I met.

194
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:39,490
So why bother asking me?

195
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:42,290
Tell me.

196
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:45,260
What exactly did Feng Suige tell you?

197
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,360
What sweet lies did he use

198
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,220
to beguile you?

199
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:49,610
Brother didn't beguile me.

200
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:52,190
He told me the truth.

201
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,380
You're still calling him "Brother"?

202
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,030
You'd rather believe his nonsense

203
00:11:57,030 --> 00:11:58,260
than believe me?

204
00:11:58,630 --> 00:12:00,110
I am your mother.

205
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,360
I'm the only family you have left

206
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,520
in this world!

207
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:03,870
That's exactly why I can't let you

208
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,130
keep making mistakes!

209
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,790
Mother,

210
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:08,480
please wake up.

211
00:12:09,390 --> 00:12:11,270
Don't stay lost in your delusions,

212
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:13,530
and don't keep making the same mistakes.

213
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,480
Listen to yourself.

214
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:18,810
What nonsense are you even talking about?

215
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:20,960
I can still tell

216
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,000
right from wrong.

217
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:23,840
I have never been

218
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,060
this clear-headed in my entire life.

219
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,120
Mother,

220
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,600
I beg you.

221
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,240
Please turn back.

222
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:34,080
You know, Grandfather's last words

223
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,750
were for me

224
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:39,320
to take good care of you.

225
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,480
I don't want to see you

226
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,080
keep making the same mistakes.

227
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,000
I don't want to see you

228
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,670
become what you are now.

229
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:48,120
Brother is still alive.

230
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,420
We still have a chance to make amends.

231
00:12:50,780 --> 00:12:52,910
Anyone in this world can say I'm wrong—

232
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:54,840
anyone but you!

233
00:12:55,510 --> 00:12:56,990
Everything I've done

234
00:12:57,670 --> 00:12:59,200
has been for you.

235
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,320
Mother.

236
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,390
I've made my decision.

237
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:10,150
I'll issue an edict to strip Murong Yao

238
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:13,000
of his position as
the Imperial Guards' Commander-in-Chief.

239
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,400
Even if you try to stop me,

240
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,200
I'll still do it.

241
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,890
I was wrong indeed.

242
00:13:22,390 --> 00:13:24,010
My mistake was

243
00:13:24,610 --> 00:13:25,880
spoiling you too much.

244
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:29,770
You're not yet ready to bear
the weight of an emperor.

245
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,520
I was too hasty.

246
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:34,680
From this moment on,

247
00:13:35,510 --> 00:13:37,390
you'll remain in the palace
to reflect on your mistakes.

248
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,200
You're not to take a single step outside.

249
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:41,200
I will handle court affairs in your stead,

250
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,480
and matters of state
will be decided by me.

251
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,410
The rest can wait

252
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,800
until you've truly reflected on
your actions.

253
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:13,310
[May the Noble Spirit Endure]

254
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:16,900
[Embrace Simplicity and Uphold Truth]

255
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:18,730
Father,

256
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:20,160
where are you going?

257
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,940
Have you found Feng Suige?

258
00:14:26,540 --> 00:14:28,760
Feng Suige is now isolated and weak.

259
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,050
If he wants to compete against us,

260
00:14:31,050 --> 00:14:34,210
[Embrace Simplicity and Uphold Truth]

261
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,240
the Feng Battalion

262
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:32,870
is the only power

263
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:33,930
he can rely on.

264
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,710
I've decided

265
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:38,440
to go to the Feng Battalion
to personally take command.

266
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:38,910
Father,

267
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,590
I'll go with you.

268
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:42,520
No need.

269
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:46,270
You lead the Imperial Guards
and stay in the capital.

270
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:48,030
As long as the capital stays secure

271
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:50,080
and the Feng Battalion
is under my control,

272
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,100
Feng Suige

273
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:52,750
will sooner or later

274
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:54,550
be trapped like a turtle in a jar.

275
00:14:55,260 --> 00:14:58,630
[Embrace Simplicity and Uphold Truth]

276
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,600
Alright,

277
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,950
don't worry too much.

278
00:14:59,070 --> 00:15:01,650
Everything is under my control.

279
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:03,000
Feng Suige

280
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,750
has no chance of turning the tables.

281
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,120
Alright, Father.

282
00:15:07,210 --> 00:15:08,270
Please be careful.

283
00:15:14,370 --> 00:15:14,900
Let's go!

284
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,560
Why did you summon me?

285
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:49,080
You're the first person to ever see me

286
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,680
draw a bow and shoot an arrow.

287
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:53,030
What do you think?

288
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:54,910
How does my heroic stance

289
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,440
compare to your brother's?

290
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:01,260
You can't even fully draw the bow.

