Now in this palace,

574
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,880
even I find it difficult to protect you.

575
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:35,620
You'd better go outside
and hide for a while.

576
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:38,100
I've arranged a residence in the city.

577
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:39,440
Go and stay there.

578
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:44,390
Don't forget,

579
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,970
you were the one who reminded me

580
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:49,720
the Qianqiu Festival is approaching.

581
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:52,130
You should start preparing early.

582
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:58,270
Thank you for your kindness, Mother.

583
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,160
I understand.

584
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,670
And I know what to do.

585
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:04,060
Don't disappoint me again this time.

586
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:13,780
Your Highness!

587
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:17,000
The antidote.

588
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:19,120
Give me the antidote.

589
00:30:19,270 --> 00:30:19,680
Yes.

590
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,110
I said before

591
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,070
that these antidotes must not be touched

592
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:32,670
until the grand plan begins.

593
00:30:36,310 --> 00:30:36,960
And now,

594
00:30:39,350 --> 00:30:41,150
the grand plan is about to begin.

595
00:32:47,370 --> 00:32:48,640
Feng Suige...

596
00:32:49,110 --> 00:32:50,550
Uncle Murong.

597
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:54,220
We meet again.

598
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,770
So you really aren't dead.

599
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:59,200
With my great vengeance unavenged,

600
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,880
how would I dare to die first?

601
00:33:10,580 --> 00:33:11,510
There's no rush.

602
00:33:12,550 --> 00:33:14,210
I still have things to ask you.

603
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:16,630
There's nothing left to say.

604
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:18,000
Kill him!

605
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:46,980
You once saved my life.

606
00:33:48,140 --> 00:33:50,690
I regarded you as my closest elder.

607
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:54,650
Why did you kill my father?

608
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:58,380
Why did you want me dead as well?

609
00:33:58,920 --> 00:33:59,720
If you hadn't,

610
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,820
then Yao would have had to die.

611
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:03,970
I begged you,

612
00:34:05,250 --> 00:34:06,510
but you turned me down.

613
00:34:07,590 --> 00:34:09,290
You wouldn't help me save Yao.

614
00:34:10,110 --> 00:34:12,170
I carried thorny branches on my back,

615
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:15,460
kowtowing with every step into the palace,

616
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:17,480
to beg your father

617
00:34:17,510 --> 00:34:18,860
to spare his life.

618
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:22,070
But he still wouldn't let Yao go.

619
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,710
I couldn't just watch

620
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:28,230
my son die.

621
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,820
Yao and I

622
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:33,000
had no way out.

623
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:35,400
This was all

624
00:34:36,690 --> 00:34:39,360
forced upon us by you and your father.

625
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:42,580
If it hadn't been for Murong Yao's

626
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,800
treason and collusion with the enemy,

627
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,230
so many Susha soldiers

628
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:47,400
wouldn't have died unjustly

629
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,860
in the Battle of Pingling!

630
00:34:56,110 --> 00:34:57,360
He betrayed me.

631
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,100
I could spare his life,

632
00:35:01,510 --> 00:35:03,110
but how am I supposed to answer to

633
00:35:03,110 --> 00:35:05,170
all our brothers who died?

634
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:13,340
Talking about

635
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:15,070
brotherhood in front of me?

636
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:21,490
In this life,

637
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:25,050
how many battles

638
00:35:26,430 --> 00:35:27,420
have Yao and I

639
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:29,760
fought for

640
00:35:31,180 --> 00:35:32,910
you and your father's kingdom?

641
00:35:33,770 --> 00:35:36,300
I was even like a brother to His Majesty.

642
00:35:37,030 --> 00:35:38,360
It's fair to say I've spent my entire life

643
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,960
laying down my life for him!

644
00:35:41,490 --> 00:35:42,580
Look at me!

645
00:35:43,630 --> 00:35:44,920
I've done far more for Susha

646
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,320
than you ever have.

647
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:49,040
All that talk of patriotism

648
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:51,070
is nothing

649
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:53,550
but a joke to me now!

650
00:35:54,390 --> 00:35:55,280
In my life,

651
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:57,330
I've never sought fame

652
00:35:58,400 --> 00:35:59,850
or power.

653
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,000
All I wanted

654
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:05,290
was to live peacefully

655
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:07,710
with my children and grandchildren.

656
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:11,550
Is that too much to ask?

657
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:15,150
Is that a crime?

658
00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:21,960
Your father

659
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,760
deserved to die,

660
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:38,920
and so do you.

661
00:36:43,370 --> 00:36:44,590
I must save Yao.

662
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:48,290
I must save Yao!

663
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,760
I must save Yao.

664
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,150
Suige,

665
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,910
please spare Yao.

666
00:37:46,190 --> 00:37:46,850
Killing you

667
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:49,660
was my idea.

668
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:52,330
He was forced into it.

669
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:55,230
You may pulverize my bones

670
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:57,880
and scatter my ashes.

671
00:37:58,660 --> 00:37:59,720
I only beg you

672
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:02,840
to spare Yao...

673
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:13,290
Uncle Murong.

674
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,720
His Majesty never intended

675
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:19,330
to harm you and Yao.

676
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:28,170
That day,

677
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,030
it was Empress Zhuang

678
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:33,960
who killed His Majesty.

679
00:39:06,110 --> 00:39:08,400
The Murong family has brought chaos
to our kingdom

680
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,730
and committed treason.

681
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:11,800
Their crimes are grave,

682
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:13,660
intolerable to heaven and earth.

683
00:39:14,070 --> 00:39:15,800
All soldiers, heed my command!

684
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:16,590
Yes!

685
00:39:18,190 --> 00:39:19,850
March with me into Yujing City

686
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:23,990
to avenge His Majesty!

687
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:25,150
Yes!

688
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:37,720
My mistake

689
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,700
was spoiling you too much.

690
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:42,900
You're not yet ready to bear
the weight of an emperor.

691
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:44,210
I was too hasty.

692
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:46,650
From this moment on,

693
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:48,760
you'll remain in the palace
to reflect on your mistakes.

694
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:51,020
You're not to take a single step outside.

695
00:39:51,330 --> 00:39:52,470
Spare my mother.

696
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:55,140
I'll take her away from Yujing

697
00:39:55,150 --> 00:39:56,880
to live out our remaining days.

698
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:57,710
Her sins

699
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:58,880
are also my sins.

700
00:40:00,670 --> 00:40:02,330
I'll pay for them in her place.

701
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:04,360
Someone!

702
00:40:06,440 --> 00:40:07,400
Summon the Keeper of the Imperial Seal

703
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:08,920
to bring the Imperial Seal.

704
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:10,250
I need to draft an edict.

705
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:13,110
I'm speaking to you.

706
00:40:13,150 --> 00:40:14,170
Can't you hear me?

707
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:16,130
Are you defying my orders?

708
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:17,800
Your Majesty.

709
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:18,990
Her Majesty...

710
00:40:18,990 --> 00:40:20,520
The Empress Dowager's words are orders,

711
00:40:20,520 --> 00:40:21,960
and mine aren't?

712
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:24,070
I am the Emperor.

713
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:24,760
My words—

714
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:27,360
every single word I utter
is an imperial edict!

715
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:30,530
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

716
00:40:38,940 --> 00:40:40,800
I will say this one last time.

717
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:44,070
Summon the Keeper of the Imperial Seal
to bring the Imperial Seal.

718
00:40:44,070 --> 00:40:45,480
I need to draft an edict!

719
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,930
If these ears of yours cannot hear,

720
00:40:50,710 --> 00:40:52,110
I'll cut them off for you!

721
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:00,700
Who let the Prince of Zhennan go?

722
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:07,030
Was it you?

723
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:08,820
Spare me, Your Majesty!

724
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:10,570
I know nothing about it!

725
00:41:14,020 --> 00:41:15,080
He glanced at you.

726
00:41:15,180 --> 00:41:16,110
So it must be you.

727
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:17,360
It wasn't me, Your Majesty.

728
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:18,480
Spare me, Your Majesty!

729
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:19,800
It was me who let him go.

730
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,000
All of you, leave!

731
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:34,400
Mother, what's that supposed to mean?

732
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:35,930
I should be asking you.

733
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,670
You intend to reclaim all military power.

734
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:40,330
What's that supposed to mean?

735
00:41:45,670 --> 00:41:48,150
Mother, you truly have eyes and ears
everywhere.

736
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:50,400
My edict just reached the Secretariat,

737
00:41:50,590 --> 00:41:52,150
and you're already alarmed.

738
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:52,590
Do you realize

739
00:41:52,590 --> 00:41:53,850
how much trouble

740
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,670
issuing this imperial edict will cause?

741
00:41:55,670 --> 00:41:57,510
Which of those veteran generals,
so used to wielding their own troops,

742
00:41:57,510 --> 00:41:58,970
will let it slide quietly?

743
00:41:59,230 --> 00:42:01,280
Even if the sky fell on Jinxiu,

744
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:04,850
it should be me bearing the weight.

745
00:42:05,690 --> 00:42:06,690
I understand now.

746
00:42:07,370 --> 00:42:08,360
In your heart,

747
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:10,480
the one who holds up

748
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,070
the sky over Jinxiu has never been me,

749
00:42:12,070 --> 00:42:13,600
but Xia Jingshi. Am I right?

750
00:42:13,670 --> 00:42:14,840
He did hold it up.

751
00:42:15,550 --> 00:42:16,550
If it weren't for him,

752
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:17,550
Susha's army

753
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:19,070
would have reached here long ago!

754
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:21,530
Even without Xia Jingshi,
there's still me!

755
00:42:21,630 --> 00:42:22,590
Look at

756
00:42:22,590 --> 00:42:23,920
what you've become now.

757
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:25,360
How exactly

758
00:42:25,360 --> 00:42:25,840
did that wretched Feng Xiyang

759
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:26,880
bewitch you?

760
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,280
Don't call her wretched!

761
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:31,230
You think I'm

762
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:32,630
bewitched by her beauty?

763
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:34,000
I've seen all kinds of women, okay?

764
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,590
Then why do you protect her so fiercely?

765
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:36,440
Because she gave me

766
00:42:36,440 --> 00:42:38,000
something I've never had before.

767
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:38,800
When she was most helpless,

768
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:41,060
she asked for my help. Do you understand?

769
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:46,710
Of course you wouldn't understand.

770
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:47,500
In your eyes,

771
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:49,280
I'm nothing but someone who

772
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:51,010
wastes his life in debauchery.

773
00:42:51,590 --> 00:42:53,250
I only ascended to this throne

774
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,710
because I am your son.

775
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:01,440
Have you ever for one day

776
00:43:01,440 --> 00:43:02,300
cared about me?

777
00:43:08,550 --> 00:43:09,880
Everyone in the world thinks

778
00:43:09,880 --> 00:43:10,720
I'm useless.

779
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:12,000
After a while,

780
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,530
I started to believe it too.

781
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:15,660
I once wanted to be a good emperor,

782
00:43:16,030 --> 00:43:17,490
but no one believed in me,

783
00:43:17,800 --> 00:43:19,660
and no one had expectations of me.

784
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:22,020
Then what's the point of working so hard?

785
00:43:23,040 --> 00:43:25,500
You've always been
the true ruler of Jinxiu.

786
00:43:25,770 --> 00:43:27,570
So I could only give up on myself.

787
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,240
But Feng Xiyang doesn't think like that.

788
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:32,690
She thinks I have value.

789
00:43:32,850 --> 00:43:34,030
She's never

790
00:43:34,030 --> 00:43:35,070
tried to bewitch me.

791
00:43:35,070 --> 00:43:35,480
She's never even

792
00:43:35,480 --> 00:43:36,710
treated me kindly.

793
00:43:37,550 --> 00:43:38,630
But when she was most desperate

794
00:43:38,630 --> 00:43:39,510
and most helpless,

795
00:43:39,510 --> 00:43:41,510
she asked me to help her get revenge.

796
00:43:44,930 --> 00:43:46,330
Do you find me ridiculous

797
00:43:47,920 --> 00:43:48,580
or pitiful?

798
00:43:49,760 --> 00:43:50,980
But I don't think so.

799
00:43:53,670 --> 00:43:54,590
I like this feeling

800
00:43:54,590 --> 00:43:55,760
of being needed.

801
00:44:02,360 --> 00:44:03,590
Because I have never

802
00:44:03,590 --> 00:44:04,720
been needed before.

803
00:44:05,590 --> 00:44:06,550
All of this...

804
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:10,400
All of this was because of you,

805
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,190
Mother!

